         <div type="translation" xml:space="preserve">
           <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#jmr"> <p>. . . ] lords [of the earth] under the sun [ . . . ] fortunate, Augusti [ . . . gave?] to the city to further its prosperity [ . . . ] of themselves [ . . .
               by action of?  . . .] the distinguished [governor]
            </p></div>
